Module com.hack23.cia.web

Package com.hack23.cia.web.impl.ui.application.views.pageclicklistener

package com.hack23.cia.web.impl.ui.application.views.pageclicklistener
This package provides classes and interfaces for handling page click events within the Citizen Intelligence Agency web application. Key classes and interfaces: - AbstractClickListener: Base class for click listeners. - AbstractPageItemRendererClickListener: Base class for page item renderer click listeners. - ApplicationLoginListener: Listener for handling login events. - ChangePasswordClickListener: Listener for handling change password events. - CommitFormWrapperClickListener: Listener for wrapping form commit events. - ComplianceCheckPageItemRendererClickListener: Listener for handling compliance check page item renderer events. - DecisionFlowValueChangeListener: Listener for handling decision flow value change events. - DeleteAccountClickListener: Listener for handling delete account events. - DisableGoogleAuthenticatorCredentialClickListener: Listener for handling disable Google Authenticator credential events. - LogoutClickListener: Listener for handling logout events. - ManageUserAccountClickListener: Listener for handling manage user account events. - PageItemPropertyClickListener: Listener for handling page item property click events. - PageItemRendererClickListener: Listener for handling page item renderer click events. - RefreshDataViewsClickListener: Listener for handling refresh data views events. - RegisterUserClickListener: Listener for handling register user events. - RemoveDataClickListener: Listener for handling remove data events. - RuleViolationPageItemRendererClickListener: Listener for handling rule violation page item renderer events. - SearchDocumentClickListener: Listener for handling search document events. - SendEmailClickListener: Listener for handling send email events. - SetGoogleAuthenticatorCredentialClickListener: Listener for handling set Google Authenticator credential events. - StartAgentClickListener: Listener for handling start agent events. - UpdateApplicationConfigurationClickListener: Listener for handling update application configuration events. - UpdateSearchIndexClickListener: Listener for handling update search index events. Dependencies and relationships: - Depends on com.hack23.cia.service.api for application manager and service response classes. - Depends on com.vaadin.ui for Vaadin framework classes and interfaces. - Depends on org.slf4j for logging. - Depends on org.springframework.web.context.request for request context holder. - Depends on org.springframework.web.context.support for web application context utilities.
